got interested in playing music.

00:15:00.460 --> 00:15:01.760
They thought it was neat.

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:03.060
I don't know if they speak it.

00:15:03.060 --> 00:15:04.360
We're losing the language.

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:05.660
&gt;&gt; Right.

00:15:05.660 --> 00:15:06.960
&gt;&gt; But I think that was part of it.

00:15:06.960 --> 00:15:10.140
And also, what I've discovered now
is that people that had heard us

00:15:10.140 --> 00:15:13.300
and the older people play that
live elsewhere, outside Louisiana,

00:15:13.300 --> 00:15:16.890
