that who had this vision.

00:18:09.140 --> 00:18:11.260
And so we always strived
to do it right.

00:18:11.260 --> 00:18:13.780
I mean it was, for no
reason, we we're trying

00:18:13.780 --> 00:18:15.100 position:56%
