00:18:15.100 --> 00:18:16.780
We were trying to get the song out.

00:18:16.780 --> 00:18:20.320
It was like the first, the first
record we recorded was in France.

00:18:20.320 --> 00:18:21.620
It was just happened.

00:18:21.620 --> 00:18:22.920
I mean we were in [inaudible]
and this guy came up

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:24.890
and says, I like your music.

00:18:24.890 --> 00:18:26.190
Do you have a record?

00:18:26.190 --> 00:18:27.490
I said no.

00:18:27.490 --> 00:18:28.790
Would you like to make a record?

00:18:28.790 --> 00:18:30.090
I said yeah.

00:18:30.090 --> 00:18:31.390
And he was like the
head of [inaudible].

00:18:31.390 --> 00:18:34.550
So I said we don't
have too many days.

00:18:34.550 --> 00:18:35.850
No problem.

00:18:35.850 --> 00:18:37.570
But the really first record

00:18:37.570 --> 00:18:40.760
