did we did for Floyd.

00:18:40.760 --> 00:18:42.860 position:56%
I tried to do the whole gamut of it.

00:18:42.860 --> 00:18:45.980
First of all, we had the French
and English translations.

00:18:45.980 --> 00:18:48.510
