just two steps and waltzes.

00:18:48.510 --> 00:18:49.810
There were ballads.

00:18:49.810 --> 00:18:51.110
They were tin pan alley songs.

00:18:51.110 --> 00:18:52.410
They were creole songs.

00:18:52.410 --> 00:18:53.710 position:56%
They were reels and stuff like that.

00:18:53.710 --> 00:18:56.710
Because that's what we were
learning after uncovering this

00:18:56.710 --> 00:18:59.870
